description: This file is a C header file (.h) containing macro definitions, include directives, function prototypes, and license information related to TR-104 support for MTA (Multi-Tenant Access) agents in a network device.

methods.name: mta_hal_getTR104parameterValues
methods.description: Retrieves TR-104 parameters values based on the provided parameter names list.

methods.name: mta_hal_freeTR104parameterValues
methods.description: Frees memory allocated for parameter values list.

methods.name: mta_hal_getTR104parameterNames
methods.description: Retrieves the list of TR-104 parameter names.

methods.name: TR104_open
methods.description: Initializes or opens the TR-104 support module.
